Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:16.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}找不到合适的话语　轻抚你的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:23.10,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你一言不发　冷冷挣脱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:29.64,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}小小的误解　令年轻的爱瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:36.74,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不想见你悲伤的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:43.43,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}即便抛弃梦想　请别抛弃你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:49.75,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}让它永远在我心中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.69,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}有一天　不同的你我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}携手筑起未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:04.62,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}回到曾经的地方　不论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:11.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}现在二人只有悲伤地错开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:16.66,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}相信后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:21:01.35,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:10.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:35.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:43.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:51.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:56.20,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:00.82,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾经形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:10.65,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}分别的二人　现在再也无处交集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:16.70,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾经形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:28.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}不可思议地被初次相遇的侧脸吸引困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:47.65,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾经形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:57.00,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}不用一句话语　感知你潮动的情热
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:03.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾经形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.43,0:23:07.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:18.25,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠入领海也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自凝岛是军队和曙光社所在的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星也无法窥探这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正潜入也蛮有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到那个强袭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员长什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会这样回到奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会让我们…下船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下船？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾在奥布 也有家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布确实也有住处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没人住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须说明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有击沉贵舰的最大理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国希望贵舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供强袭的所有战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并派遣其调整人驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 前往曙光社进行技术援助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请 有东西想给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布想用它干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奥布的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布不侵略他国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许他国侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 不介入他国争端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是实现这种理念的保障
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 卡嘉莉大人说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们想强化它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你的强袭那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张ID可以帮你们进入工厂一区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但再往前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有严密的个人信息验证系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时半会儿无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:30.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1172,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}基　拉
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.49,0:03:30.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1172,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}基　拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一片和平啊 街上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天领海上还发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是中立国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平之国…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没指望它大摇大摆停在军港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种级别的军舰 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能藏得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的…不在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要的是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有在的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在要有不在的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军港和曙光社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海岸边戒备森严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有设法从内部调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这国家确实没外表那么善良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家人见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 眼下这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法让你们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管时间短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午 批准在军队总部见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么现在就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天通知大家详细安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到这个名字 我还以为是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你键盘敲得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来是基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身衣服没认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们说工厂里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿军装不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你这样的公主真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天跑这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一口一个公主的 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没把人家当公主看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌被人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我终于明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时卡嘉莉 出现在曙光社的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说曙光社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赫利奥波利斯替地球军造机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟父亲说 不被理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己跑去确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你父亲不知情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…阿斯哈代表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部是有人这么传
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲自己没否认过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这种事不重要」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「责任全在自己」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我那么相信父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁流体插口的损耗严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱动系统全这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件都超负荷运作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体叫苦不迭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多东西没能保住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就参加了抵抗组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时冲动 离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说我太不了解世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就去瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠里的人战斗都很勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那片满地黄沙的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护家园 拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是奥布却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么强大的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背地里还做着那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还想在PLANT和地球联合面前扮好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太卑鄙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉想打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想让战争结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 打是打不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔 多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛  好样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大和夫妇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌兹米大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为再不会见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是命运的捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 别闹了特利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿就好 等下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者你先去吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉的家人也来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作比想像得要难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做完会耽误大天使号出航…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 同情我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁也不来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凭什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这种人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难过的人是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的人是你才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤单的基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为战斗难过 为保护不了难过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要被你这种人同情！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样了 别再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船在这里停留多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么一定要去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 是我们志愿参军的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然这么决定我不会反对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论遇到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都不会把真相告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括兄妹的事…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然略显残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样对基拉好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都遵照当初的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我们最后一次见乌兹米大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知也让人畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实就是 孩子们在一无所知的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必想得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如果动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们会察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他今天为什么不来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用「不想见」来解释…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过编辑新的量子子程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让神经突触融合的代谢速度提高40%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为适应一般自然人的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改写了离子泵的分子构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这么短时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这孩子还真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我驾驶也能开成那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错少校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想试一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅葱 下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去强袭那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 过会见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告诉我 你干什么愁眉苦脸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你拒绝和家人见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见了面又怎样 我现在是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们给喷射器推进力提升了18%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得看下面板控制参数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算军人 也是爹娘养的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母一定想你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整天做着这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶机动战士战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助开发和维护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等离开奥布 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上又要和扎夫特战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火炮的遮蔽问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子溅射处理还要30分钟完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了记得做下评估 别忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在见面的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕忍不住说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄成调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 特利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比军港管得还严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能想办法混过安检
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好几层 相当费时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个能进去的人也许更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓 披着羊皮的狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这啥玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机器鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那个人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底飞到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯…兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好朋友送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暂的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须面对的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间之舟永远航向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个名为未来的未知海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮火的巨浪重新掀起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝在浪涛下的悲鸣声是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目睹新的悲剧发生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰和基拉会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命运之杵」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显露峥嵘吧 高达
